WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.208 --> 00:00:01.543
HubSpot exists to help

00:00:01.543 --> 00:00:03.336
small businesses grow better.

00:00:03.336 --> 00:00:05.005
We were an early adopter of Claude,

00:00:05.005 --> 00:00:07.132
and we knew that this was

00:00:07.132 --> 00:00:08.717
just a fundamental change

00:00:08.717 --> 00:00:10.093
to the way we would work,

00:00:10.093 --> 00:00:11.428
and that it would impact

00:00:11.428 --> 00:00:12.554
how all of our customers

00:00:12.554 --> 00:00:13.513
at HubSpot work.

00:00:17.976 --> 00:00:20.061
What we saw pretty early on

00:00:20.061 --> 00:00:21.396
was Claude’s ability

00:00:21.396 --> 00:00:22.230
and immediately

00:00:22.230 --> 00:00:24.149
it did a superior job

00:00:24.149 --> 00:00:25.942
compared to some of the other tools

00:00:25.942 --> 00:00:27.861
that we were developing or trying.

00:00:27.861 --> 00:00:29.654
Claude has really good taste,

00:00:29.654 --> 00:00:31.656
and marketing's all about taste.

00:00:31.656 --> 00:00:33.616
And the first product pages

00:00:33.616 --> 00:00:34.701
that I was seeing

00:00:34.701 --> 00:00:36.870
just felt uniquely on brand.

00:00:36.870 --> 00:00:38.747
I gave Claude a call transcript,

00:00:38.747 --> 00:00:39.873
a couple of knowledge-based articles,

00:00:39.873 --> 00:00:42.125
and the first output was amazing.

00:00:42.125 --> 00:00:43.585
It genuinely felt like

00:00:43.585 --> 00:00:45.128
it was my voice.

00:00:45.128 --> 00:00:47.005
I felt that I was working with

00:00:47.005 --> 00:00:48.631
a strategic partner.

00:00:48.631 --> 00:00:50.050
We had a hospitality business

00:00:50.050 --> 00:00:52.177
that was struggling with their revenue

00:00:52.177 --> 00:00:53.428
in terms of

00:00:53.428 --> 00:00:55.055
where can we find cost savings?

00:00:55.055 --> 00:00:56.514
Claude was able to

00:00:56.514 --> 00:00:57.640
take the reporting

00:00:57.640 --> 00:00:58.892
from the historical standpoint

00:00:58.892 --> 00:01:00.018
and say,

00:01:00.018 --> 00:01:01.478
here's where we see

00:01:01.478 --> 00:01:03.188
your best performing weekends.

00:01:03.188 --> 00:01:04.481
Here are the weekends

00:01:04.481 --> 00:01:06.649
that were not performing as well.

00:01:06.649 --> 00:01:07.817
That is something

00:01:07.817 --> 00:01:09.861
so far beyond my typical

00:01:09.861 --> 00:01:11.279
role as a CSM.

00:01:11.279 --> 00:01:12.655
My customers are saying like,

00:01:12.655 --> 00:01:14.074
this is the best conversation

00:01:14.074 --> 00:01:15.700
I've ever had with HubSpot.

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:16.868
The time it takes

00:01:16.868 --> 00:01:18.453
to maintain some of the code base

00:01:18.453 --> 00:01:20.121
has been reduced dramatically.

00:01:20.121 --> 00:01:21.581
From idea to prototype

00:01:21.581 --> 00:01:23.666
has decreased massively.

00:01:23.666 --> 00:01:25.585
I feel like my job hasn't been

00:01:25.585 --> 00:01:27.462
this fun in a long time.

00:01:27.462 --> 00:01:29.422
The biggest change has been

00:01:29.422 --> 00:01:31.174
the ability of developers

00:01:31.174 --> 00:01:32.759
to free up some time

00:01:32.759 --> 00:01:34.427
for really value adding

00:01:34.427 --> 00:01:35.929
feature development.

00:01:35.929 --> 00:01:37.222
Claude Code has helped me

00:01:37.222 --> 00:01:39.057
become a better engineer.

00:01:39.057 --> 00:01:40.308
I feel like it has helped

00:01:40.308 --> 00:01:42.769
amplify my expertise.

00:01:42.769 --> 00:01:45.730
We've seen a 40% increase in productivity.

00:01:45.730 --> 00:01:48.108
You really feel it across a team

00:01:48.108 --> 00:01:49.859
when you get that much leverage

00:01:49.859 --> 00:01:50.860
in the work you're doing.

00:01:50.860 --> 00:01:52.570
We get to help the businesses

00:01:52.570 --> 00:01:54.114
that shape the world

00:01:54.114 --> 00:01:55.615
 and shape the economy.

00:01:55.615 --> 00:01:56.699
HubSpot and Anthropic

00:01:56.699 --> 00:01:58.409
have an amazing shared mission,

00:01:58.409 --> 00:02:01.788
which we can give people access to tools

00:02:01.788 --> 00:02:04.624
and information to build their businesses

00:02:04.624 --> 00:02:07.502
in a way that just wasn't before possible.

